quran[12{c,v,t}:
35,19,andha aur aankhon wala barabar nahi hai
35,20,nah tarikhiyan aur roshni yaksaa hain
35,21,nah thandhi chaon aur dhoop ki tapish aik jaisi hai
35,22,"aur nah زندے aur murdy masawi hain Allah jisay chahta hai سنواتا hai, magar ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum unn logon ko nahi suna satke jo qabron mein madfoon hain"
35,23,tum to bas aik khabardaar karne walay ho
35,24,hum ne tum ko haq ke sath bheja hai basharat dainay wala aur darane wala bana kar aur koi ummat aisi nahi guzri hai jis mein koi mutnabba karne wala nah aaya ho
35,25,ab agar yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain to inn se pehlay guzray hue log bhi jhutla chuke hain unn ke paas un ke rasool khulay dalail aur saheefay aur roshan Hadayat dainay wali kitaab le kar aeye thay
35,26,phir jin logon ne nah maana unn ko mein ne pakar liya aur dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi
35,27,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah aasman se pani barsata hai aur phir is ke zareya se hum terhan terhan ke phal nikaal laatay hain jin ke rang mukhtalif hotay hain pahoron mein bhi safaid, surkh aur gehri siyah daharian payi jati hain jin ke rang mukhtalif hotay hain"
35,28,aur isi terhan insanon aur janwaron aur maweshion ke rang bhi mukhtalif hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ke bundon mein se sirf ilm rakhnay walay log hi uss se drtay hain be shak Allah zabardast aur dar guzar frmane wala hai
35,29,"jo log kitaab Allah ki talawat karte hain aur namaz qaim karte hain, aur jo kuch hum ne unhen rizaq diya hai is mein se khulay aur chupay kharch karte hain, yaqeenan woh aik aisi tijarat ke mutawaqqa hain jis mein hargiz khasara nah hoga"
35,30,( is tijarat mein unhon ne apna sab kuch iss liye khappaya hai ) taakay Allah unn ke ajar poooray ke poooray unn ko day aur mazeed apne fazl se un ko ataa farmaiye be shak Allah bakhsnay wala aur qadar daan hai
